Preconditions:
- The input matrix `grid` is not null.
- The dimensions of the input matrix `grid` are even integers.
- The value of `k` is a positive integer.

Postconditions:
- The output matrix has the same dimensions as the input matrix `grid`.
- The elements in each layer of the output matrix are cyclically rotated `k` times in the counter-clockwise direction.
- The output matrix is returned.